(57, 1, '2013-06-24 05:54:59', '2013-06-24 05:54:59', '<pre id="line1">These days, many kids draw little distinction between real life and online life. They may use social websites designed for children such as Webkinz or Club Penguin, or social websites designed for adults such as Windows Live Spaces, YouTube, MySpace, Flickr, Twitter, Facebook, and others. Whatever they''re doing, they should understand that many of these web pages can be viewed by anyone with access to the Internet.</pre>', 'How to help your kids use social websites more safely', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'how-to-help-your-kids-use-social-websites-more-safely', '', '', '2013-06-24 06:03:57', '2013-06-24 06:03:57', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=57', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(58, 1, '2013-06-24 05:54:48', '2013-06-24 05:54:48', '', 'How to help your kids use social websites more safely', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '57-revision', '', '', '2013-06-24 05:54:48', '2013-06-24 05:54:48', '', 57, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=58', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(59, 1, '2013-06-24 05:55:32', '2013-06-24 05:55:32', '<pre id="line1">The recommended age for signing up for social websites is usually 13 and over. If your children are under the recommended age for these sites, do not let them use the sites. It is important to remember that you cannot rely on the services themselves to keep your underage child from signing up..</pre>', 'Ensure your kids follow age limits on the site', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ensure-your-kids-follow-age-limits-on-the-site', '', '', '2013-06-24 06:03:39', '2013-06-24 06:03:39', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=59', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(60, 1, '2013-06-24 05:55:23', '2013-06-24 05:55:23', '', 'Ensure your kids follow age limits on the site', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '59-revision', '', '', '2013-06-24 05:55:23', '2013-06-24 05:55:23', '', 59, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=60', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(61, 1, '2013-06-24 05:56:01', '2013-06-24 05:56:01', 'Operating System is the important program that runs on the computer. It performs basic tasks like recognizing the input from the keyboard, controlling various files and directories in the hard disk and also various peripheral devices like printers, scanners etc...It will control the program in such a way that they do not interfere with one another.It is responsible for securing the system by not allowing the unauthorized users to access the system.', 'Operating System Security', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'operating-system-security', '', '', '2013-07-17 07:39:41', '2013-07-17 07:39:41', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=61', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(62, 1, '2013-06-24 05:55:50', '2013-06-24 05:55:50', '', 'Operating System Security', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '61-revision', '', '', '2013-06-24 05:55:50', '2013-06-24 05:55:50', '', 61, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=62', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(63, 1, '2013-06-24 05:56:29', '2013-06-24 05:56:29', 'Passwords control access to files, programs, computers, hard drives and networks. They also deny access to unauthorized users. Poorly chosen passwords make it easier to break into your computer systems and expose to malicious attacks. In general, set up passwords and keep them secret never share it with others.', 'Use Strong Passwords', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'use-strong-passwords', '', '', '2013-07-17 07:39:17', '2013-07-17 07:39:17', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=63', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(64, 1, '2013-06-24 05:56:19', '2013-06-24 05:56:19', '', 'Use Strong Passwords', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '63-revision', '', '', '2013-06-24 05:56:19', '2013-06-24 05:56:19', '', 63, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=64', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(65, 1, '2013-06-24 05:56:56', '2013-06-24 05:56:56', 'Spam is usually unwanted e-mail advertising about a product sent to list of e-mails or group of e-mail addresses. Generally spamming companies send e-mails to thousands of email addresses every day without confirming whether e-mail addresses are real or not .When ever you open a spam mail it alerts the spammer at the other end and confirms that email address is real and is active. This will continue to spam and sometimes directory of such email addresses are sold to other companies.', 'One of the common risk through e-mails is SPAM', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'one-of-the-common-risk-through-e-mails-is-spam', '', '', '2013-07-17 07:38:45', '2013-07-17 07:38:45', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=65', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(66, 1, '2013-06-24 05:56:46', '2013-06-24 05:56:46', '', 'One of the common risk through e-mails is SPAM', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '65-revision', '', '', '2013-06-24 05:56:46', '2013-06-24 05:56:46', '', 65, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=66', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(67, 1, '2013-06-24 05:57:56', '2013-06-24 05:57:56', '<pre id="line1">Spam is usually unwanted e-mail advertising about a product sent to list of e-mails or group of e-mail addresses. Generally spamming companies send e-mails to thousands of email addresses every day without confirming whether e-mail addresses are real or not .When ever you open a spam mail it alerts the spammer at the other end and confirms that email address is real and is active. This will continue to spam and sometimes directory of such email addresses are sold to other companies..</pre>', 'One of the common risk through e-mails is SPAM', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '65-autosave', '', '', '2013-06-24 05:57:56', '2013-06-24 05:57:56', '', 65, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=67', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(68, 1, '2013-06-24 05:56:56', '2013-06-24 05:56:56', '<pre id="line1">Spam is usually unwanted e-mail advertising about a product sent to list of e-mails or group of e-mail addresses. Generally spamming companies send e-mails to thousands of email addresses every day without confirming whether e-mail addresses are real or not .When ever you open a spam mail it alerts the spammer at the other end and confirms that email address is real and is active. This will continue to spam and sometimes directory of such email addresses are sold to other companies..</pre>', 'One of the common risk through e-mails is SPAM', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '65-revision-2', '', '', '2013-06-24 05:56:56', '2013-06-24 05:56:56', '', 65, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=68', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(69, 1, '2013-06-24 05:56:29', '2013-06-24 05:56:29', '<pre id="line1">Passwords control access to files, programs, computers, hard drives and networks. They also deny access to unauthorized users. Poorly chosen passwords make it easier to break into your computer systems and expose to malicious attacks. In general, set up passwords and keep them secret never share it with others.</pre>', 'Use Strong Passwords', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '63-revision-2', '', '', '2013-06-24 05:56:29', '2013-06-24 05:56:29', '', 63, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=69', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(70, 1, '2013-06-24 05:56:01', '2013-06-24 05:56:01', '<pre id="line1">Operating System is the important program that runs on the computer. It performs basic tasks like recognizing the input from the keyboard, controlling various files and directories in the hard disk and also various peripheral devices like printers, scanners etc...It will control the program in such a way that they do not interfere with one another.It is responsible for securing the system by not allowing the unauthorized users to access the system.</pre>', 'Operating System Security', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '61-revision-2', '', '', '2013-06-24 05:56:01', '2013-06-24 05:56:01', '', 61, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=70', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(71, 1, '2013-06-24 05:55:32', '2013-06-24 05:55:32', '<pre id="line1">The recommended age for signing up for social websites is usually 13 and over. If your children are under the recommended age for these sites, do not let them use the sites. It is important to remember that you cannot rely on the services themselves to keep your underage child from signing up..</pre>', 'Ensure your kids follow age limits on the site', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '59-revision-2', '', '', '2013-06-24 05:55:32', '2013-06-24 05:55:32', '', 59, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=71', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
