(135, 1, '2013-07-02 14:07:10', '2013-07-02 14:07:10', '<br></br>\r\nLearning to pick strong passwords and protect them appropriately is an important part. Why? Because passwords are still a primary means of authenticating your identity --a way to prove that you are really you to computers and networks.', 'Picking and Protecting Password', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'picking-and-protecting-password', '', '', '2013-07-18 10:27:43', '2013-07-18 10:27:43', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=135', 0, 'post', '', 0),
