(274, 1, '2013-07-02 14:08:02', '2013-07-02 14:08:02', '<pre id="line1">Email services bring many benefits. It''s an easy and convenient way to communicate with colleagues and with customers. But email is not an inherently secure medium of communication. It poses large security risks if used improperly.</pre>', 'Safer Emailing and Instant messaging', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '138-revision-2', '', '', '2013-07-02 14:08:02', '2013-07-02 14:08:02', '', 138, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=274', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
