(296, 1, '2013-07-17 07:37:50', '2013-07-17 07:37:50', 'Learning to pick strong passwords and protect them appropriately is an important part. Why? Because passwords are still a primary means of authenticating your identity --a way to prove that you are really you to computers and networks.', 'Picking and Protecting Password', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '135-revision-4', '', '', '2013-07-17 07:37:50', '2013-07-17 07:37:50', '', 135, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=296', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
