agement</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n	<li>Risk management</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Risks Management</li>\r\n	<li>Continuous Service Management</li>\r\n	<li>Information Security Management</li>\r\n	<li>Monitor, Evaluate and  Assess Internal Control</li>\r\n	<li>Compliance with External requirements</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n	<li>Resource management\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Human Resource management</li>\r\n	<li>IT resource procurement</li>\r\n	<li>Configuration management</li>\r\n	<li>Data management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Performance management\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Define and manage service level</li>\r\n	<li>IT performance, capacity and conformance</li>\r\n	<li>Management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 'IT Governance', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '316-revision-5', '', '', '2013-07-29 06:19:34', '2013-07-29 06:19:34', '', 316, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=323', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(321, 1, '2013-07-29 05:54:02', '2013-07-29 05:54:02', 'IT Governance is to:\r\n<div>•Directs and controls IT resource uses in line with strategic goal</div>\r\n<div>•Process to leverage IT resources and to ensure the value delivery, managing risk and performance</div>\r\n<div>•Process for evaluation , selection and prioritization of IT investment</div>\r\nThere are many definitions of IT Governance\r\n\r\nGartner defines “IT governance (ITG) as the processes that ensure the effective and efficient use of IT in enabling an organization to achieve its goals. It is the process by which organizations ensure the effective evaluation, selection, prioritization, and funding of competing IT investments; oversee their implementation; and extract (measurable) business benefits.”\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nEnterprise IT governance is the process by\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Which decisions are made  around IT investments.</li>\r\n	<li>How decisions are made,</li>\r\n	<li>Who makes the decisions,</li>\r\n	<li>Who is held accountable</li>\r\n	<li>How the results of  decisions are measured  and monitored and</li>\r\n	<li>What value to be delivered to meet company goal</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBenefits of  IT Governance\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Aligned Support Business</li>\r\n	<li>Secured controlled IT risk</li>\r\n	<li>Faster delivery time</li>\r\n	<li>Cheaper service cost</li>\r\n	<li>Better Service quality</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIT Governance focus area:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Strategic Alignment\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Strategic IT plan and Roadmap</li>\r\n	<li>Communication and understanding</li>\r\n	<li>Quality management system</li>\r\n	<li>Project management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Value Delivery\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Budget and cost management</li>\r\n	<li>\r\nDevelop, Acquire and Maintain Application Software</li>\r\n	<li>\r\nChanges Management</li>\r\n	<li>\r\nChanges Acceptance and Transition Management</li>\r\n	<li>\r\nService Desk and Incidents Management</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Problems Management</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Risk management\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Risks Management</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Continuous Service Management</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Information Security Management</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Monitor, Evaluate and  Assess Internal Control</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Compliance with External requirements</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Resource management\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Human Resource management</li>\r\n	<li>IT resource procurement</li>\r\n	<li>Configuration management</li>\r\n	<li>Data management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Performance management\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Define and manage service level</li>\r\n	<li>IT performance, capacity and conformance</li>\r\n	<li>Management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 'IT Governance', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '316-revision-3', '', '', '2013-07-29 05:54:02', '2013-07-29 05:54:02', '', 316, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=321', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(318, 1, '2013-07-29 05:50:31', '2013-07-29 05:50:31', ' ', '', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '318', '', '', '2013-08-29 08:28:15', '2013-08-29 08:28:15', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=318', 28, 'nav_menu_item', '', 0),
(322, 1, '2013-07-29 05:55:04', '2013-07-29 05:55:04', 'IT Governance is to:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Directs and controls IT resource uses in line with strategic goal</li>\r\n	<li>Process to leverage IT resources and to ensure the value delivery, managing risk and performance</li>\r\n	<li>Process for evaluation , selection and prioritization of IT investment</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThere are many definitions of IT Governance\r\n\r\nGartner defines “IT governance (ITG) as the processes that ensure the effective and efficient use of IT in enabling an organization to achieve its goals. It is the process by which organizations ensure the effective evaluation, selection, prioritization, and funding of competing IT investments; oversee their implementation; and extract (measurable) business benefits.”\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nEnterprise IT governance is the process by\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Which decisions are made  around IT investments.</li>\r\n	<li>How decisions are made,</li>\r\n	<li>Who makes the decisions,</li>\r\n	<li>Who is held accountable</li>\r\n	<li>How the results of  decisions are measured  and monitored and</li>\r\n	<li>What value to be delivered to meet company goal</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBenefits of  IT Governance\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Aligned Support Business</li>\r\n	<li>Secured controlled IT risk</li>\r\n	<li>Faster delivery time</li>\r\n	<li>Cheaper service cost</li>\r\n	<li>Better Service quality</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIT Governance focus area:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Strategic Alignment\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Strategic IT plan and Roadmap</li>\r\n	<li>Communication and understanding</li>\r\n	<li>Quality management system</li>\r\n	<li>Project management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Value Delivery\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Budget and cost management</li>\r\n	<li>Develop, Acquire and Maintain Application Software</li>\r\n	<li>Changes Management</li>\r\n	<li>Changes Acceptance and Transition Management</li>\r\n	<li>Service Desk and Incidents Management</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Problems Management</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Risk management\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Risks Management</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Continuous Service Management</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Information Security Management</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Monitor, Evaluate and  Assess Internal Control</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Compliance with External requirements</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Resource management\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Human Resource management</li>\r\n	<li>IT resource procurement</li>\r\n	<li>Configuration management</li>\r\n	<li>Data management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Performance management\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Define and manage service level</li>\r\n	<li>IT performance, capacity and conformance</li>\r\n	<li>Management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 'IT Governance', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '316-revision-4', '', '', '2013-07-29 05:55:04', '2013-07-29 05:55:04', '', 316, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=322', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(320, 1, '2013-07-29 05:47:24', '2013-07-29 05:47:24', 'IT Governance is to:\r\n<div>•Directs and controls IT resource uses in line with strategic goal</div>\r\n<div>•Process to leverage IT resources and to ensure the value delivery, managing risk and performance</div>\r\n<div>•Process for evaluation , selection and prioritization of IT investment</div>\r\nThere are many definitions of IT Governance\r\n\r\nGartner defines “IT governance (ITG) as the processes that ensure the effective and efficient use of IT in enabling an organization to achieve its goals. It is the process by which organizations ensure the effective evaluation, selection, prioritization, and funding of competing IT investments; oversee their implementation; and extract (measurable) business benefits.”\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nEnterprise IT governance is the process by\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Which decisions are made  around IT investments.</li>\r\n	<li>How decisions are made,</li>\r\n	<li>Who makes the decisions,</li>\r\n	<li>Who is held accountable</li>\r\n	<li>How the results of  decisions are measured  and monitored and</li>\r\n	<li>What value to be delivered to meet company goal</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBenefits of  IT Governance\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Aligned Support Business</li>\r\n	<li>Secured controlled IT risk</li>\r\n	<li>Faster delivery time</li>\r\n	<li>Cheaper service cost</li>\r\n	<li>Better Service quality</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIT Governance focus area:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Strategic Alignment\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Strategic IT plan and Roadmap</li>\r\n	<li>Communication and understanding</li>\r\n	<li>Quality management system</li>\r\n	<li>Project management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Value Delivery\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Budget and cost management</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Develop, Acquire and Maintain Application Software</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Changes Management</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Changes Acceptance and Transition Management</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Service Desk and Incidents Management</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Problems Management</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Risk management\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Risks Management</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Continuous Service Management</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Information Security Management</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Monitor, Evaluate and  Assess Internal Control</div></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<div>Compliance with External requirements</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Resource management\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Human Resource management</li>\r\n	<li>IT resource procurement</li>\r\n	<li>Configuration management</li>\r\n	<li>Data management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Performance management\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Define and manage service level</li>\r\n	<li>IT performance, capacity and conformance</li>\r\n	<li>Management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 'IT Governance', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '316-revision-2', '', '', '2013-07-29 05:47:24', '2013-07-29 05:47:24', '', 316, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=320', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
