(416, 1, '2013-08-28 13:53:36', '2013-08-28 13:53:36', '<style type="text/css"><!--\r\n@page { margin: 0.79in }\r\n		P { margin-bottom: 0.08in }\r\n--></style><span style="font-family: Times New Roman,serif;"><span style="font-size: medium;">After a recent conversation explaining the relationship between a standard and guideline, I thought I’d post this diagram which clearly shows the relationship, at that of policies and procedures.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/policy-standard-guideline-and-procedure.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-415" alt="policy, standard, guideline, and procedure" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/policy-standard-guideline-and-procedure-237x300.jpg" width="464" height="586" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Times New Roman,serif;"><span style="font-size: medium;">Source: CISA Certified Information Systems Auditor Study Guide</span></span>', 'Relationship between a policy, standard, guideline, and procedure', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '414-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-08-28 13:53:36', '2013-08-28 13:53:36', '', 414, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=416', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(417, 1, '2013-08-28 13:54:36', '2013-08-28 13:54:36', '<style type="text/css"><!--\r\n@page { margin: 0.79in }\r\n		P { margin-bottom: 0.08in }\r\n--></style><span style="font-family: Times New Roman,serif;"><span style="font-size: medium;">After a recent conversation explaining the relationship between a standard and guideline, I thought I’d post this diagram which clearly shows the relationship, at that of policies and procedures.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/policy-standard-guideline-and-procedure.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-415" alt="policy, standard, guideline, and procedure" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/policy-standard-guideline-and-procedure-237x300.jpg" width="464" height="586" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Times New Roman,serif;"><span style="font-size: medium;">Source: CISA Certified Information Systems Auditor Study Guide</span></span>', 'Relationship between a policy, standard, guideline, and procedure', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '414-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-08-28 13:54:36', '2013-08-28 13:54:36', '', 414, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=417', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
