(23, 2, 7, 'Question: 8', 1, 'In password protection, this is a random string of data\r\nused to modify a password hash.', 'It''s Right.In password protection, salt is a random string of data\r\nused to modify a password hash. Salt can also be\r\nadded to make it more difficult for an attacker to\r\nbreak into a system by using password hash-\r\nmatching strategies because adding salt to a\r\npassword hash prevents an attacker from testing\r\nknown dictionary words across the entire system', 'Sorry :( -The correct answer is B) salt. In\r\npassword protection, salt is a random string of data\r\nused to modify a password hash. Salt can also be\r\nadded to make it more difficult for an attacker to\r\nbreak into a system by using password hash-\r\nmatching strategies because adding salt to a\r\npassword hash prevents an attacker from testing\r\nknown dictionary words across the entire system', 0, 0, '', 'single', 0, 0, 'a:4:{i:0;O:27:"WpProQuiz_Model_AnswerTypes":7:{s:10:"\0*\0_answer";s:9:" sheepdip";s:8:"\0*\0_html";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_points";i:1;s:11:"\0*\0_correct";b:0;s:14:"\0*\0_sortString";s:0:"";s:18:"\0*\0_sortStringHtml";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_mapper";N;}i:1;O:27:"WpProQuiz_Model_AnswerTypes":7:{s:10:"\0*\0_answer";s:4:"salt";s:8:"\0*\0_html";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_points";i:1;s:11:"\0*\0_correct";b:1;s:14:"\0*\0_sortString";s:0:"";s:18:"\0*\0_sortStringHtml";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_mapper";N;}i:2;O:27:"WpProQuiz_Model_AnswerTypes":7:{s:10:"\0*\0_answer";s:6:"bypass";s:8:"\0*\0_html";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_points";i:1;s:11:"\0*\0_correct";b:0;s:14:"\0*\0_sortString";s:0:"";s:18:"\0*\0_sortStringHtml";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_mapper";N;}i:3;O:27:"WpProQuiz_Model_AnswerTypes":7:{s:10:"\0*\0_answer";s:6:"dongle";s:8:"\0*\0_html";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_points";i:1;s:11:"\0*\0_correct";b:0;s:14:"\0*\0_sortString";s:0:"";s:18:"\0*\0_sortStringHtml";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_mapper";N;}}', 0, 0, 0),
(24, 2, 8, 'Question: 9', 1, 'This is a mode of operation for a block cipher, with the\r\ncharacteristic that each possible block of plaintext has\r\na defined corresponding ciphertext value and vice', 'Correct. Electronic Code Book (ECB) is a mode of operation\r\nfor a block cipher, with the characteristic that each possible\r\nblock of plaintext has a defined corresponding ciphertext\r\nvalue and vice versa. In other words, the same plaintext value\r\nwill always result in the same ciphertext value.', 'Sorry :( -The correct answer is D) Electronic Code\r\nBook. Electronic Code Book (ECB) is a mode of operation\r\nfor a block cipher, with the characteristic that each possible\r\nblock of plaintext has a defined corresponding ciphertext\r\nvalue and vice versa. In other words, the same plaintext value\r\nwill always result in the same ciphertext value.', 0, 0, '', 'single', 0, 0, 'a:4:{i:0;O:27:"WpProQuiz_Model_AnswerTypes":7:{s:10:"\0*\0_answer";s:12:"footprinting";s:8:"\0*\0_html";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_points";i:1;s:11:"\0*\0_correct";b:0;s:14:"\0*\0_sortString";s:0:"";s:18:"\0*\0_sortStringHtml";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_mapper";N;}i:1;O:27:"WpProQuiz_Model_AnswerTypes":7:{s:10:"\0*\0_answer";s:14:" hash function";s:8:"\0*\0_html";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_points";i:1;s:11:"\0*\0_correct";b:0;s:14:"\0*\0_sortString";s:0:"";s:18:"\0*\0_sortStringHtml";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_mapper";N;}i:2;O:27:"WpProQuiz_Model_AnswerTypes":7:{s:10:"\0*\0_answer";s:9:"watermark";s:8:"\0*\0_html";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_points";i:1;s:11:"\0*\0_correct";b:0;s:14:"\0*\0_sortString";s:0:"";s:18:"\0*\0_sortStringHtml";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_mapper";N;}i:3;O:27:"WpProQuiz_Model_AnswerTypes":7:{s:10:"\0*\0_answer";s:20:"Electronic code Book";s:8:"\0*\0_html";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_points";i:1;s:11:"\0*\0_correct";b:1;s:14:"\0*\0_sortString";s:0:"";s:18:"\0*\0_sortStringHtml";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_mapper";N;}}', 0, 0, 0),
(25, 2, 9, 'Question: 10', 1, 'This is a trial and error method used to decode\r\nencrypted data through exhaustive effort rather than\r\nemploying intellectual strategies.', 'Correct. Just as a criminal might break into, or\r\n"crack" a safe by trying many possible combinations, a\r\nbrute force cracking application proceeds through all\r\npossible combinations of legal characters in sequence.\r\nBrute force is considered to be an infallible, although\r\ntime-consuming, approach.', 'Sorry :( -The correct answer is D) brute force\r\ncracking Just as a criminal might break into, or\r\n"crack" a safe by trying many possible combinations, a\r\nbrute force cracking application proceeds through all\r\npossible combinations of legal characters in sequence.\r\nBrute force is considered to be an infallible, although\r\ntime-consuming, approach.', 0, 0, '', 'single', 0, 0, 'a:4:{i:0;O:27:"WpProQuiz_Model_AnswerTypes":7:{s:10:"\0*\0_answer";s:22:"chaffing and winnowing";s:8:"\0*\0_html";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_points";i:1;s:11:"\0*\0_correct";b:0;s:14:"\0*\0_sortString";s:0:"";s:18:"\0*\0_sortStringHtml";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_mapper";N;}i:1;O:27:"WpProQuiz_Model_AnswerTypes":7:{s:10:"\0*\0_answer";s:13:"cryptanalysis";s:8:"\0*\0_html";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_points";i:1;s:11:"\0*\0_correct";b:0;s:14:"\0*\0_sortString";s:0:"";s:18:"\0*\0_sortStringHtml";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_mapper";N;}i:2;O:27:"WpProQuiz_Model_AnswerTypes":7:{s:10:"\0*\0_answer";s:11:"serendipity";s:8:"\0*\0_html";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_points";i:1;s:11:"\0*\0_correct";b:0;s:14:"\0*\0_sortString";s:0:"";s:18:"\0*\0_sortStringHtml";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_mapper";N;}i:3;O:27:"WpProQuiz_Model_AnswerTypes":7:{s:10:"\0*\0_answer";s:20:"brute force cracking";s:8:"\0*\0_html";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_points";i:1;s:11:"\0*\0_correct";b:1;s:14:"\0*\0_sortString";s:0:"";s:18:"\0*\0_sortStringHtml";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_mapper";N;}}', 0, 0, 0),
(26, 5, 2, 'Question: 3', 1, 'In your work for the BC government, you occasionally have to use email to send personal, private information (such as social security numbers, medical data or dates of birth) to third party service provider (agency or organization).What is the best way to protect the information?', 'That''s right!Actually, every one of the\r\nitems should be done each time you have to share personal\r\ninformation. It is best practice to encrypt the information -\r\nencryption is the conversion of data into a form called ciphertext\r\nthat cannot be easily understood without decrypting it to its\r\noriginal form. Learn more from a previous quiz on encryption.', 'Sorry - The correct answer is E). Actually, every one of the\r\nitems should be done each time you have to share personal\r\ninformation. It is best practice to encrypt the information -\r\nencryption is the conversion of data into a form called ciphertext\r\nthat cannot be easily understood without decrypting it to its\r\noriginal form. Learn more from a previous quiz on encryption.', 0, 0, '', 'single', 0, 0, 'a:5:{i:0;O:27:"WpProQuiz_Model_AnswerTypes":7:{s:10:"\0*\0_answer";s:58:"Check for an information sharing agreement for directions.";s:8:"\0*\0_html";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_points";i:1;s:11:"\0*\0_correct";b:0;s:14:"\0*\0_sortString";s:0:"";s:18:"\0*\0_sortStringHtml";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_mapper";N;}i:1;O:27:"WpProQuiz_Model_AnswerTypes":7:{s:10:"\0*\0_answer";s:70:"If it has been awhile, ask your manager if there are new instructions.";s:8:"\0*\0_html";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_points";i:1;s:11:"\0*\0_correct";b:0;s:14:"\0*\0_sortString";s:0:"";s:18:"\0*\0_sortStringHtml";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_mapper";N;}i:2;O:27:"WpProQuiz_Model_AnswerTypes":7:{s:10:"\0*\0_answer";s:52:"Encrypt the information before sending it via email.";s:8:"\0*\0_html";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_points";i:1;s:11:"\0*\0_correct";b:0;s:14:"\0*\0_sortString";s:0:"";s:18:"\0*\0_sortStringHtml";b:0;s:10:"\0*\0_mapper";N;}i:3;O:27:"WpProQuiz_Model_AnswerTypes